# S07-T06: Integration Tests

## Objective
End-to-end flows via Playwright: WebSocket reconnect, stream source switching, HUD rendering, replay timeline.

## Acceptance Criteria
- `e2e/reconnect.spec.ts` — kill MSW WS, verify reconnect with banner state changes.
- `e2e/source-switch.spec.ts` — switch camera↔WebRTC↔replay without HUD remount.
- `e2e/hud-render.spec.ts` — radar + gauges visible at 1920×1080.
- `e2e/replay.spec.ts` — load fixture session, scrub, verify telemetry replay.

## Steps
1. Author specs leveraging MSW handlers + fixture data.
2. Add helper `expectHudVisible(page)` selector group.
3. Add latency probe — assert frame painted under threshold.
4. Wire into CI script.

## Invariants
- Tests run against `pnpm preview` (production-like build).
- No network egress; all backends mocked.
- Failures attach trace + screenshot.
